headline: Jacobs Named Construction Manager as Advisor of Fermilab's DUNE Near Site
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was named the Construction Manager as Advisor (CMa) for the Long-Baseline Neutrino Facility (LBNF) Near Site Conventional Facilities project located at the U.S. Department of Energy's Fermi National Accelerator Laboratory (Fermilab) in Batavia, Illinois.
